[? if budget <= 0: Chancellor [+ chancellor +] responds to the banking crisis with more cuts to welfare. ?][? if budget > 0: Surprisingly, Chancellor [+ chancellor +] has refrained from cutting social spending, owing to the budget surplus, and has taken measures to stabilize the economy and banking system.  ?] [? if budget <= 0: As we are firmly in opposition to the current cabinet, we have free rein to rally against these austerity measures. ?]


